cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation evaluation metrics. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel approach using a dependency parsing model. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves similarity measures, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses a neural network model for dependency parsing.
